__Summary__:test packaging-dir feature

__Precondition__

1. Tested Pkgs: fake
2. Tested Repo: https://download.tizendev.org/snapshots/trunk/common/latest
3. Tested Conf: conf_fixtures/tizendev.cfg

__Steps__

> sudo rm ~/GBS-ROOT/local/repos -rf

> rm build -rf

> mkdir build

> cd build/

> ../tools/create_proj ../specs/fake.spec

> cd fake

> git mv packaging anything

> git commit -m "change packaging dirname to anything"

> gbs -c ../../conf_fixtures/tizendev.cfg build --packaging-dir=anything -A ia32 2>&1 | tee ../log

> cd ..

#check build log key word init_buildsystem...--spec xxx.spec
> test -n "`grep "init_buildsystem.*fake.spec" log`"

#check source package whether changed or not
> cd fake && test -n "`git status | grep "working directory clean"`"

#check rpm generated whether or not
> test -n "`find ~/GBS-ROOT/local/repos -name "*fake*.rpm"`"

